{"type":"message","id":"7c8f0fa6","parentId":"2c581370","timestamp":"2026-02-13T17:53:44.309Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"WAXPEER interface initialized. I have mapped the primary API and WebSocket documentation for integration.\n\n### Core Connection Details\n*   **Base API URL:** `https://api.waxpeer.com/v1`\n*   **Swagger Docs:** `https://api.waxpeer.com/docs`\n*   **WebSockets:**\n    *   **Market Data:** `wss://waxpeer.com/socket.io/?EIO=4&transport=websocket` (Socket.IO)\n    *   **Trade Controller:** `wss://wssex.waxpeer.com` (Standard WS)\n\n### Initial Requirements for Sale Mode\nDue to Steam's API updates, the following are now required to maintain an \"Online\" status:\n1.  **Steam Access Token:** Must be sent via POST to `/v1/user/steam-token` at least once per hour.\n2.  **Authentication:** WebSocket connections require an `auth` object containing `waxAPI`, `steamid`, and `tradeurl`.\n3.  **Trade Confirmation:** It is mandatory to react to the `send-trade` and `cancelTrade` events via the Trade Controller websocket.\n\n### Ready for Next Command\nI can now proceed with:\n*   Fetching current inventory/prices.\n*   Setting up automated buy/sell logic.\n*   Monitoring specific items via the Socket.IO feed.\n\nHow would you like to proceed?","textSignature":"EjQKMgG+Pvb7j2EsH+fkXl/3wd9sJVYFGBom3VJH94zG5kYW2myvqxb8u3HunGieDCFPzkWJ"}],"api":"google-generative-ai","provider":"google","model":"gemini-3-flash-preview","usage":{"input":48104,"output":303,"cacheRead":16314,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48407,"cost":{"input":0.024052,"output":0.000909,"cacheRead":0.0008157,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0257767}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771005220635}}
